      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the firm, the funding, the house... all of it. i just lost everything in the crash and the debt is so high i dont even see a way out. but more than the money, it's the shame. i can't even think about going back and looking my parents or my employees in the eye. i'm just a complete failure and i feel like a stain on everyone i love.",
