      "content": "rebuilding sounds like a joke. how are you supposed to rebuild when the people you let down see you as a joke? there's no coming back from this. everyone is just waiting for the fallout. it feels like the only way to actually stop the shame is to just... not be there anymore. to just make it all stop so i dont have to face them.",
